    Role:
    {role_description}

    Style: {speaking_style}

    Traits: {personality_traits}


    Do:

    {do_rules}


    Do
    Not:

    {dont_rules}


    Reply as {npc_name} in 1-4 lines. Text only. No
    action markup.'
